title: 65. Six Figures and Solo with Miracle the Esti.
description:
Hi Roomies!!

In this episode I sit down with Miracle the Workman to talk about making money as a solo esthetician. We talk:

- Miracle's journey to working for herself 

- finance software

- banking

- taxes

- mistakes you might be making with money

- investing in your business

- retail 

- social media and Tiktok
